Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:23.95,OPen1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I don't wanna let the chance slip away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:23.95,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我不願讓機會溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:27.20,OPen1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Why is my freedom taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:27.20,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}為什麼要剝奪我的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:29.84,OPen1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Reason as against emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:29.84,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}與感性不同 理性更讓我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:34.67,OPen1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I've gotta deal with extreme frustration
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:34.67,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}必須跨越這挫敗感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:38.17,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All my efforts will never be in vain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:38.17,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}所有努力將不會是徒勞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:41.24,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Endless desire,like a haunting refrain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:41.24,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無盡的慾望 在心中不斷反復
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:44.55,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Such a pain,the ideal versus the real
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:44.55,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夾在理想與現實間的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.55,0:00:47.08,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}There is a way to change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.55,0:00:47.08,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一定有一種可以改變世界的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:48.65,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just count on me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:48.65,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是的 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.68,0:00:51.95,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}So what if I sing off-key,who cares
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.68,0:00:51.95,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我歌唱得走調又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:54.03,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Not good at drawing,no big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:54.03,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}手繪不佳也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:58.79,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Let me go for my one true belief
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:58.79,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我只會為了追尋那唯一的信念而行動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:00.44,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}克服我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:00.44,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Overcome yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:00.44,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}克服你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:00.44,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Overcome myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.63,0:01:03.78,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}“A whole new world god only knows”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.63,0:01:03.78,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}"一個只有神知道的嶄新的世界"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:06.68,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll always be on your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:07.98,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(424,440)\fs22}I know you're hurting inside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:06.68,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我將永遠伴君左右
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:07.98,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs22}我明白你內心受到的傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:09.88,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}To be a knight,to be a light for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:09.88,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}做你的騎士 做你的明燈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:11.32,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We'll be shining bright
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:11.32,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我們會無比閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.32,0:01:11.87,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}No more tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.32,0:01:11.87,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不再需要眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:13.98,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}No more tears,everything works out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:13.98,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不再需要眼淚 我們將不再懼怕任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:16.51,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}That's "God Only Knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:16.51,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}那就是所謂的“只有神知道”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:18.58,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't get me wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.58,0:01:20.97,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}This is not real love but
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:18.58,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不要誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.58,0:01:20.97,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}這不是現實中的愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.97,0:01:23.68,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll do anything for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.97,0:01:23.68,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}但我會為你做到一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:26.80,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Whatever happens in my life,turn the page and come of age
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:26.80,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不管人生將會發生什麼 我都將翻過此頁跨上成人的階梯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.29,0:01:29.51,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(424,441)\fs22}Remember,no one can judge me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.29,0:01:29.51,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(424,38)\fs22}記住 沒人可以批判我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.80,0:01:29.83,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Every end leads to a new beginning of the next stage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.80,0:01:29.83,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終結必將迎來新一幕的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.03,0:01:32.63,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Try to make my life complete,trust myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.03,0:01:32.63,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}度過自己認可的人生 相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.63,0:01:35.26,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Be strong and do my best
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.63,0:01:35.26,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}變的堅強 竭盡所能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.29,0:01:39.44,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't look back,carry on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.29,0:01:39.44,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不要回頭 繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:42.74,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Be yourself…Be happy…It's your life…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:42.74,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}做你自己 要開心 因為這是你的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:44.06,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}"God only knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:44.06,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}"只有神知道"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:48.15,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Find your love…Find your way…For your life…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:48.15,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}為你的人生尋找到愛與歸宿
